<emphasis id="33A7CD77FF82395AEBD2C269FD115E42" bold="true" box="[227,750,1370,1397]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Stratigraphic and geographic distribution</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="016C1165FF82395AEBD2C2B9FD665EFE" blockId="44.[227,1436,1418,1480]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
Lutetian: Weches Formation and “Stone City beds”, 
<collectingRegion id="C317DF87FF82395AE845C2B9FC435E92" box="[884,956,1418,1444]" country="United States of America" name="Texas" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Texas</collectingRegion>
. Bartonian: Wheelock Member, 
<collectingRegion id="C317DF87FF82395AEE61C2B9FA675E92" box="[1360,1432,1418,1444]" country="United States of America" name="Texas" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Texas</collectingRegion>
; “upper” Lisbon Formation, 
<collectingRegion id="C317DF87FF82395AE916C29DFD6A5EFE" box="[551,661,1454,1480]" country="United States of America" name="Alabama" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Alabama</collectingRegion>
.
</paragraph>
